      "description": "Offered is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2-liter inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Recent mechanical preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement and a precision valve clearance adjustment. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers to maintain the chassis's renowned handling characteristics. While the paint displays minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain is mechanically sound, pulling hard to the 8,000 RPM redline with a crisp exhaust note. A true driver\u2019s car for the discerning enthusiast.",
